author: Danny Daniels
title: Redskins sweep Rabun County
text:
Redskins sweep Rabun County   
SOCIAL CIRCLE — Social Circle took a giant step toward defending its Region 8-AA softball championship Wednesday with a sweep of Rabun County in the league’s tournament semifinals.
